# The monthly range bet: when the tape is calm, sell both sides and buy
# wings for defined risk. The condor collects if price stays inside the
# short strikes; the wings cap the damage if it doesn't. Rolling at 21
# DTE rebuilds the whole structure at fresh strikes.

strategy "Monthly Iron Condor"

universe $SPY

when [quiet 2%]
  write [iron_condor delta=20 width=5 dte=45]

close at [profit 50%]
  or [loss 200%]

roll at [dte 21]

risk [contracts 1]
